3.00	Young_and_dangerous	Young and Dangerous (series)	The Young and Dangerous film series (Chinese: ) is a collection of Hong Kong films about a group of triad young members, detailing their adventures, dangers and growth in a Hong Kong triad society. The series is based on a popular comic book series known as "Teddy Boy".	http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/b/b2/Young_and_Dangerous_%28series%29_DVD_cover.jpg
